Starting Docker

Docker is key component of Containers.
Currently Docker supports two platform - Linux, Window
It creates, manages and even orchastrate the container
This concept was started with dotCloud under Platform as a service. The tool created to manage this PAAS is names as Docker.
Docker is short form of Dock Worker(someone who loads and unloads cargo from ship).

Docker technology have 03 core sub parts 
1. The runtime
2. The Daemon ( a.k.a engine )
3. The Orchastrator

